b"Hey, #KubotaCountry. If you're new around here, welcome to the family! We use #KubotaCountry frequently and thought we'd breakdown a little bit more of it's meaning this week. First off, Kubota Country is not one place or one story. Rather, it is the culmination of moments that come together over time to tell our story in progress. It\xe2\x80\x99s where we are drawn together by a kindred spirit, a community with shared interests and entrepreneurial drive, to celebrate the lives we live and the work we do, one moment at a time and from one town to the next. 

Kubota Country is the familiar. Kubota Country is the land where you operate. Kubota Country is multi-generational. Kubota County is an ongoing story written by you- Kubota Country IS you. 

#KubotaCountry #KubotaUSA #MyKubotaCan #KubotaTractors"
